-energy Kondo model) at both the high- and low-magnetic\nfield limits. Perhaps most importantly, we provide a single coherent picture\nfor the host of phenomena to which this model has been applied.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Oct 2006 19:06:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
